  "texts": [
    "In this section, some key challenges and corresponding future directions are discussed in the hope of motivating further research endeavors for VLM-based HRC systems.",
    "The pretraining and deployment of VLMs in practical manufacturing scenes face significant challenges, primarily due to the high computational demands and extensive data requirements for training these models.",
    "Obtaining high-quality, annotated data sets in diverse manufacturing environments is costly and time-consuming.",
    "Additionally, effective HRC applications require real-time processing, but VLMs often face latency issues.",
    "Meanwhile, in real-life production scenarios, VLMs must also be robust and reliable to handle variations and ambiguities effectively."
  ],
